<br>
If you move your mouse just at the top of the up arrow in the upper chat window if should turn to a double arrow pointing lower left to upper right. Hold down the left mouse button and pull up until you have the size you want. Next move your mouse over the bar in the center window and pull it up until you have the two windows the size you want.<br>
